pageProduct.description:

General Information

Swisse Ultiboost Iron is a premium quality formula to help maintain healthy blood and prevent dietary iron deficiency.

Healthy Blood: Iron and vitamin B6 assist healthy red blood cell production. Iron also helps maintain transport of oxygen in the body and supports blood health.

Tiredness & Fatigue Relief: Iron, vitamin B6 and vitamin C help relieve tiredness and fatigue.

Iron Absorption: Vitamin C supports absorption of dietary iron.

Lifestyle Claim: Vegetarian

Size: 30 Packs

Warnings

Not for the treatment of iron deficiency conditions. If symptoms persist consult your healthcare practitioner. Vitamins can only be of assistance if the dietary vitamin intake is inadequate.

Ingredients

EACH TABLET CONTAINS:

Iron (from iron amino acid chelate) 20 mg

Vitamin C (as ascorbic acid from calcium ascorbate dihydrate) 16.52 mg

Vitamin B6 (as pyridoxine from pyridoxine hydrochloride) 8.22 mg

Betacarotene 1 mg

Certified Organic Spirulina (Arthrospira platensis cell powder) 200 mg

Directions

ADULT DOSAGE:

One tablet daily, during or immediately after a meal, or as directed by a healthcare professional.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 30 degrees Celsius. Do not use if cap seal is broken.
